      • getUrlTemplate

        public String getUrlTemplate()
        Get an opaque URL template to the content, which follows RFC 6570. There is an asset_path variable that should be replaced with a valid path. Valid paths are different for each representation subtype. It may change over time and should not be hard-coded or cached.
        Returns:
        url template
